---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
const personalImageAlt = "Guillermo Torrez";
---

<article
  class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row"
>
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-500 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-100 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1"
  >
    <p>
      Hey there! I'm Guillermo Torrez, originally from Nicaragua. I've got a
      knack for JavaScript Web and Mobile Development, and I've been diving into
      this exciting field since I was young.
      <strong
        >My drive for optimization and performance fuels my quest to deliver the
        ultimate user experience!</strong
      >
    </p>

    <p>
      When I'm not coding up a storm, you'll find me indulging in my passions,
      <strong
        >like diving into the pool for a swim or plotting my next chess move.</strong
      >
      They're my secret ingredients for striking the perfect work-life balance!
    </p>
    <p>Remember, in life, good or bad, this too shall pass.</p><strong
      >"Gam zeh ya'avor"</strong
    >
  </div>

  <Image
    width="200"
    height="200"
    src="/me.png"
    alt={personalImageAlt}
    class="order-1 object-cover w-64 h-full p-1 md:order-2 rotate-3 lg:p-2 lg:w-64 aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-black/20 dark:bg-yellow-500/5 ring-1 ring-yellow/70 dark:ring-yellow/50"
    style="object-position: 50% 50%"
    loading='lazy'
  />
</article>
